headline.main: ELECTION RESULTS ANALYZED BY POLL; Roosevelt Foreign Policy Hurt La Guardia, the Gallup Analysis Indicates

lead_paragraph: PRINCETON, N.J., Nov. 7 -- Tuesday's election results in two areas -- the Fifteenth Pennsylvania Congressional District and New York City -- have started a train of speculation among political observers as to the light which these elections shed on the popularity of the foreign policy of the Roosevelt Administration.
abstract: Gallup poll shows Roosevelt foreign policy cut LaGuardia vote
